items.title: Awesome Godot
items.content_text:
### Templates / Godot 4

*   [Maaack's Game Template (⭐894)](https://github.com/Maaack/Godot-Game-Template) - Template with a main menu, options menus, pause menu, credits, scene loader, extra tools, and an example game scene.

### Plugins and scripts / Godot 4

*   [Maaack's Game Template Plugin (⭐894)](https://github.com/Maaack/Godot-Game-Template) - Template with a main menu, options menus, pause menu, credits, scene loader, extra tools, and an example game scene.
*   [Maaack's Menus Template (⭐286)](https://github.com/Maaack/Godot-Menus-Template) - Template with a main menu, options menus, credits, and a scene loader.
*   [Maaack's Scene Loader (⭐50)](https://github.com/Maaack/Godot-Scene-Loader) - Scene loader that includes a loading screen, progress bar, and error handling.
